If all nodes in high priority are frozen, retry will occur in nodes with low priority. 2) If 'Retry Interval' is set, upon failure of a particular channel, it will be frozen for a period, and no one will use this channel until the freeze period ends. 3) After exhausting the retry count, the process will end directly.
